шеi<?php exit; ?>a:2:{s:7:"content";a:21:{s:10:"_edit_lock";a:1:{i:0;s:12:"1763039492:1";}s:20:"_elementor_edit_mode";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"builder";}s:24:"_elementor_template_type";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"wp-post";}s:18:"_elementor_version";a:1:{i:0;s:6:"3.33.0";}s:17:"_wp_page_template";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"default";}s:15:"_elementor_data";a:1:{i:0;s:19498:"[{"id":"e444c6d","elType":"container","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"898703b","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p data-start=\"348\" data-end=\"703\"><strong data-start=\"348\" data-end=\"360\">Resumen:<\/strong> 2025 acelera una nueva ola en v\u00eddeo online: c\u00f3decs m\u00e1s eficientes (AV1\/VVC), distribuci\u00f3n sobre <strong data-start=\"457\" data-end=\"474\">HTTP\/3 + QUIC<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"497\">latencias sub-2 s<\/strong> con LL-HLS\/DASH, producci\u00f3n cloud nativa y capas de <strong data-start=\"550\" data-end=\"556\">IA<\/strong> para upscaling, moderaci\u00f3n y personalizaci\u00f3n. Adem\u00e1s, el negocio se mueve hacia <strong data-start=\"637\" data-end=\"654\">FAST channels<\/strong>, compras integradas y experiencias interactivas.<\/p><hr data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"708\" \/><h2 data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"749\">1) Nuevos c\u00f3decs y calidad de imagen<\/h2><ul data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"1361\"><li data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"930\"><p data-start=\"752\" data-end=\"930\"><strong data-start=\"752\" data-end=\"759\">AV1<\/strong> se consolida en navegadores, Smart TV y m\u00f3viles de gama media. Permite ~<strong data-start=\"832\" data-end=\"853\">30% menos bitrate<\/strong> a igual calidad respecto a H.264\/HEVC. Ideal para VOD y cat\u00e1logos grandes.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1092\"><p data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"1092\"><strong data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"948\">VVC (H.266)<\/strong> aparece en entornos premium (Smart TV recientes, STB). Aporta hasta <strong data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1027\">40\u201350%<\/strong> de ganancia sobre HEVC, aunque con <strong data-start=\"1063\" data-end=\"1083\">coste de c\u00f3mputo<\/strong> mayor.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1093\" data-end=\"1190\"><p data-start=\"1095\" data-end=\"1190\"><strong data-start=\"1095\" data-end=\"1102\">AV2<\/strong> (en desarrollo) y <strong data-start=\"1121\" data-end=\"1128\">EVC<\/strong> ganan pilotos, pero su adopci\u00f3n masiva se empujar\u00e1 a 2026+.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1191\" data-end=\"1361\"><p data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1361\"><strong data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1211\">HDR para todos<\/strong>: HLG y HDR10+ se extienden fuera del cine\/series; deportes y eSports adoptan <strong data-start=\"1289\" data-end=\"1309\">Wide Color Gamut<\/strong> y <strong data-start=\"1312\" data-end=\"1319\">HFR<\/strong> (60\u2013120 fps) en dispositivos compatibles.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1384\"><strong data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1384\">Qu\u00e9 hacer en 2025<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"1385\" data-end=\"1573\"><li data-start=\"1385\" data-end=\"1485\"><p data-start=\"1387\" data-end=\"1485\">Mantener <strong data-start=\"1396\" data-end=\"1414\">ladder h\u00edbrido<\/strong>: H.264 (compatibilidad), AV1 (web y m\u00f3viles), HEVC\/VVC (TV premium).<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1573\"><p data-start=\"1488\" data-end=\"1573\">Probar <strong data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1502\">VVC<\/strong> en cat\u00e1logos 4K\/HDR y eventos premium donde el ahorro de CDN compense.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"1575\" data-end=\"1578\" \/><h2 data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1625\">2) Latencia ultrabaja sin romper la escala<\/h2><ul data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1889\"><li data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1714\"><p data-start=\"1628\" data-end=\"1714\"><strong data-start=\"1628\" data-end=\"1652\">Low-Latency HLS\/DASH<\/strong> consolidado con CMAF chunks (latencias <strong data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1703\">1.5\u20134 s<\/strong> reales).<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1715\" data-end=\"1798\"><p data-start=\"1717\" data-end=\"1798\"><strong data-start=\"1717\" data-end=\"1727\">WebRTC<\/strong> para interactividad <strong data-start=\"1748\" data-end=\"1759\">&lt;500 ms<\/strong> (apuestas, subastas, watch-parties).<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1889\"><p data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1889\"><strong data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1813\">SRT\/RIST<\/strong> en contribuci\u00f3n: enlaces robustos, cifrados y con recuperaci\u00f3n de paquetes.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"1891\" data-end=\"1919\"><strong data-start=\"1891\" data-end=\"1919\">Arquitectura recomendada<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"1920\" data-end=\"2151\"><li data-start=\"1920\" data-end=\"2022\"><p data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"2022\"><strong data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"1941\">Eventos masivos<\/strong>: LL-HLS\/DASH + <strong data-start=\"1957\" data-end=\"1972\">HTTP\/3\/QUIC<\/strong> + <strong data-start=\"1975\" data-end=\"1988\">Multi-CDN<\/strong> con conmutaci\u00f3n en tiempo real.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2023\" data-end=\"2151\"><p data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2151\"><strong data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2042\">Interacciones<\/strong> (c\u00e1mara del p\u00fablico, Q&amp;A, juegos): microservicios <strong data-start=\"2093\" data-end=\"2103\">WebRTC<\/strong> al borde (edge) junto a la distribuci\u00f3n LL-HLS.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"2153\" data-end=\"2156\" \/><h2 data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2210\">3) Transporte y entrega: HTTP\/3, Multi-CDN y edge<\/h2><ul data-start=\"2211\" data-end=\"2506\"><li data-start=\"2211\" data-end=\"2306\"><p data-start=\"2213\" data-end=\"2306\"><strong data-start=\"2213\" data-end=\"2230\">HTTP\/3 + QUIC<\/strong> reduce latencia de establecimiento y mejora la recuperaci\u00f3n ante p\u00e9rdida.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2307\" data-end=\"2404\"><p data-start=\"2309\" data-end=\"2404\"><strong data-start=\"2309\" data-end=\"2322\">Multi-CDN<\/strong> con orquestaci\u00f3n basada en <strong data-start=\"2350\" data-end=\"2401\">QoE (rebuffering, time-to-first-frame, errores)<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2405\" data-end=\"2506\"><p data-start=\"2407\" data-end=\"2506\"><strong data-start=\"2407\" data-end=\"2425\">Edge computing<\/strong> para personalizaci\u00f3n de manifests, blackout regional y ad-stitching server-side.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2521\"><strong data-start=\"2508\" data-end=\"2521\">Checklist<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"2522\" data-end=\"2782\"><li data-start=\"2522\" data-end=\"2579\"><p data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2579\">Activar <strong data-start=\"2532\" data-end=\"2542\">HTTP\/3<\/strong> en origen y verificar soporte CDN.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2580\" data-end=\"2690\"><p data-start=\"2582\" data-end=\"2690\">Implementar <strong data-start=\"2594\" data-end=\"2619\">orquestador Multi-CDN<\/strong> con reglas por pa\u00eds\/ISP y mediciones en vivo (Real User Monitoring).<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2691\" data-end=\"2782\"><p data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2782\">Llevar al <strong data-start=\"2703\" data-end=\"2711\">edge<\/strong>: geoblocking, tokens, watermarking ligero y manipulaci\u00f3n de manifests.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"2784\" data-end=\"2787\" \/><h2 data-start=\"2789\" data-end=\"2835\">4) Producci\u00f3n cloud nativa y automatizaci\u00f3n<\/h2><ul data-start=\"2836\" data-end=\"3114\"><li data-start=\"2836\" data-end=\"2936\"><p data-start=\"2838\" data-end=\"2936\"><strong data-start=\"2838\" data-end=\"2865\">Codificaci\u00f3n en la nube<\/strong> el\u00e1stica (spot\/preemptible) reduce CAPEX y ajusta costes por evento.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2937\" data-end=\"3004\"><p data-start=\"2939\" data-end=\"3004\"><strong data-start=\"2939\" data-end=\"2956\">Live clipping<\/strong> y highlights autom\u00e1ticos para redes sociales.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3005\" data-end=\"3114\"><p data-start=\"3007\" data-end=\"3114\"><strong data-start=\"3007\" data-end=\"3042\">Server-side ad insertion (SSAI)<\/strong> con segmentaci\u00f3n por dispositivo\/ubicaci\u00f3n manteniendo latencias bajas.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3287\"><strong data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3127\">Consejo<\/strong>: separar <strong data-start=\"3137\" data-end=\"3150\">workloads<\/strong> (live, VOD catch-up, clipping) en colas distintas; aplicar <strong data-start=\"3210\" data-end=\"3225\">autoscaling<\/strong> por m\u00e9tricas reales (input queue depth, CPU, dropped frames).<\/p><hr data-start=\"3289\" data-end=\"3292\" \/><h2 data-start=\"3294\" data-end=\"3319\">5) IA aplicada a v\u00eddeo<\/h2><ul data-start=\"3320\" data-end=\"3783\"><li data-start=\"3320\" data-end=\"3416\"><p data-start=\"3322\" data-end=\"3416\"><strong data-start=\"3322\" data-end=\"3343\">Upscaling\/Enhance<\/strong> (super-resoluci\u00f3n): mejora nitidez percibida y recorta bitrate 10\u201320%.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3417\" data-end=\"3494\"><p data-start=\"3419\" data-end=\"3494\"><strong data-start=\"3419\" data-end=\"3443\">Detecci\u00f3n de escenas<\/strong> para ABR m\u00e1s eficiente y thumbnails autom\u00e1ticos.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3495\" data-end=\"3600\"><p data-start=\"3497\" data-end=\"3600\"><strong data-start=\"3497\" data-end=\"3511\">Moderaci\u00f3n<\/strong> y <strong data-start=\"3514\" data-end=\"3535\">an\u00e1lisis de marca<\/strong> (logos, objetos) para compliance y reporting a patrocinadores.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3601\" data-end=\"3688\"><p data-start=\"3603\" data-end=\"3688\"><strong data-start=\"3603\" data-end=\"3629\">Subt\u00edtulos autom\u00e1ticos<\/strong> + traducci\u00f3n en tiempo real: accesibilidad sin fricci\u00f3n.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3689\" data-end=\"3783\"><p data-start=\"3691\" data-end=\"3783\"><strong data-start=\"3691\" data-end=\"3722\">Personalizaci\u00f3n de portadas<\/strong> y recomendaciones h\u00edbridas (contenido + contexto de sesi\u00f3n).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"3785\" data-end=\"3788\" \/><h2 data-start=\"3790\" data-end=\"3816\">6) Seguridad y derechos<\/h2><ul data-start=\"3817\" data-end=\"4130\"><li data-start=\"3817\" data-end=\"3926\"><p data-start=\"3819\" data-end=\"3926\"><strong data-start=\"3819\" data-end=\"3840\">DRM multi-sistema<\/strong> (Widevine, FairPlay, PlayReady) + <strong data-start=\"3875\" data-end=\"3900\">rotaci\u00f3n de licencias<\/strong> y <strong data-start=\"3903\" data-end=\"3923\">tokens de acceso<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"3927\" data-end=\"4035\"><p data-start=\"3929\" data-end=\"4035\"><strong data-start=\"3929\" data-end=\"3954\">Forensic watermarking<\/strong> en eventos premium para trazar filtraciones sin penalizar al usuario leg\u00edtimo.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"4036\" data-end=\"4130\"><p data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4130\"><strong data-start=\"4038\" data-end=\"4063\">DDoS y bot mitigation<\/strong> en capa de aplicaci\u00f3n y CDN (tokens cortos, challenge progresivo).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"4132\" data-end=\"4135\" \/><h2 data-start=\"4137\" data-end=\"4184\">7) Negocio: FAST, shoppable e interactividad<\/h2><ul data-start=\"4185\" data-end=\"4581\"><li data-start=\"4185\" data-end=\"4290\"><p data-start=\"4187\" data-end=\"4290\"><strong data-start=\"4187\" data-end=\"4204\">FAST channels<\/strong> (canales lineales gratuitos con publicidad) crecen con contenido archivado + clips.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"4291\" data-end=\"4391\"><p data-start=\"4293\" data-end=\"4391\"><strong data-start=\"4293\" data-end=\"4312\">CTV advertising<\/strong> madura: segmentaci\u00f3n household-level, frecuencia control y <strong data-start=\"4372\" data-end=\"4388\">medici\u00f3n MRC<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"4392\" data-end=\"4476\"><p data-start=\"4394\" data-end=\"4476\"><strong data-start=\"4394\" data-end=\"4413\">Shoppable video<\/strong>: overlays clicables y sincronizaci\u00f3n con cat\u00e1logo eCommerce.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"4477\" data-end=\"4581\"><p data-start=\"4479\" data-end=\"4581\"><strong data-start=\"4479\" data-end=\"4504\">Interactividad nativa<\/strong>: encuestas, reacciones, rankings en vivo y <strong data-start=\"4548\" data-end=\"4580\">sincronizaci\u00f3n second-screen<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"4583\" data-end=\"4586\" \/><h2 data-start=\"4588\" data-end=\"4636\">8) M\u00e9tricas de calidad (QoE) y sostenibilidad<\/h2><ul data-start=\"4637\" data-end=\"4917\"><li data-start=\"4637\" data-end=\"4768\"><p data-start=\"4639\" data-end=\"4768\"><strong data-start=\"4639\" data-end=\"4663\">M\u00e1s all\u00e1 del bitrate<\/strong>: medir <strong data-start=\"4671\" data-end=\"4689\">rebuffer ratio<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"4691\" data-end=\"4707\">startup time<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"4709\" data-end=\"4732\">playtime por sesi\u00f3n<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"4734\" data-end=\"4765\">errores por dispositivo\/ISP<\/strong>.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"4769\" data-end=\"4917\"><p data-start=\"4771\" data-end=\"4917\"><strong data-start=\"4771\" data-end=\"4793\">Optimizaci\u00f3n verde<\/strong>: elecci\u00f3n de c\u00f3decs eficientes, segment durations equilibradas y <strong data-start=\"4859\" data-end=\"4886\">alimentar CDNs cercanas<\/strong> para minimizar hops y consumo.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"4919\" data-end=\"4922\" \/><h2 data-start=\"4924\" data-end=\"4955\">9) 5G\/6G, Spatial Video y XR<\/h2><ul data-start=\"4956\" data-end=\"5236\"><li data-start=\"4956\" data-end=\"5035\"><p data-start=\"4958\" data-end=\"5035\"><strong data-start=\"4958\" data-end=\"4967\">5G SA<\/strong> mejora uplink para creativos m\u00f3viles (mochilas de bonding + SRT).<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5036\" data-end=\"5139\"><p data-start=\"5038\" data-end=\"5139\"><strong data-start=\"5038\" data-end=\"5058\">Spatial Video\/VR<\/strong>: pruebas de <strong data-start=\"5071\" data-end=\"5084\">180\u00b0\/360\u00b0<\/strong> y c\u00e1maras <strong data-start=\"5095\" data-end=\"5111\">volum\u00e9tricas<\/strong> para conciertos\/deportes.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5140\" data-end=\"5236\"><p data-start=\"5142\" data-end=\"5236\"><strong data-start=\"5142\" data-end=\"5164\">Render en el borde<\/strong> (edge rendering) para experiencias XR ligeras en dispositivos modestos.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"5238\" data-end=\"5241\" \/><h2 data-start=\"5243\" data-end=\"5287\">Arquitectura de referencia 2025 (resumen)<\/h2><ol data-start=\"5288\" data-end=\"5749\"><li data-start=\"5288\" data-end=\"5335\"><p data-start=\"5291\" data-end=\"5335\"><strong data-start=\"5291\" data-end=\"5302\">Ingesta<\/strong>: SRT\/RIST \u2192 Origen redundante.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5336\" data-end=\"5414\"><p data-start=\"5339\" data-end=\"5414\"><strong data-start=\"5339\" data-end=\"5360\">Transcodificaci\u00f3n<\/strong>: Cloud nativa (H.264\/AV1\/HEVC\/VVC), packaging CMAF.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5415\" data-end=\"5504\"><p data-start=\"5418\" data-end=\"5504\"><strong data-start=\"5418\" data-end=\"5434\">Distribuci\u00f3n<\/strong>: LL-HLS\/DASH sobre <strong data-start=\"5454\" data-end=\"5464\">HTTP\/3<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"5466\" data-end=\"5479\">Multi-CDN<\/strong> con orquestador y RUM.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5505\" data-end=\"5566\"><p data-start=\"5508\" data-end=\"5566\"><strong data-start=\"5508\" data-end=\"5526\">Interactividad<\/strong>: WebRTC paralelo con SFU\/MCU en edge.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5567\" data-end=\"5618\"><p data-start=\"5570\" data-end=\"5618\"><strong data-start=\"5570\" data-end=\"5586\">Monetizaci\u00f3n<\/strong>: SSAI + DRMs + reporting CTV.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5619\" data-end=\"5676\"><p data-start=\"5622\" data-end=\"5676\"><strong data-start=\"5622\" data-end=\"5635\">Seguridad<\/strong>: tokens cortos, watermarking, WAF\/CDN.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5677\" data-end=\"5749\"><p data-start=\"5680\" data-end=\"5749\"><strong data-start=\"5680\" data-end=\"5698\">Observabilidad<\/strong>: dashboard QoE + alertas por pa\u00eds\/ISP\/dispositivo.<\/p><\/li><\/ol><hr data-start=\"5751\" data-end=\"5754\" \/><h2 data-start=\"5756\" data-end=\"5785\">Roadmap pr\u00e1ctico (90 d\u00edas)<\/h2><p data-start=\"5787\" data-end=\"5801\"><strong data-start=\"5787\" data-end=\"5801\">Semana 1\u20132<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"5802\" data-end=\"5903\"><li data-start=\"5802\" data-end=\"5863\"><p data-start=\"5804\" data-end=\"5863\">Activar <strong data-start=\"5812\" data-end=\"5822\">HTTP\/3<\/strong> y pruebas <strong data-start=\"5833\" data-end=\"5843\">LL-HLS<\/strong> en preproducci\u00f3n.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5864\" data-end=\"5903\"><p data-start=\"5866\" data-end=\"5903\">Integrar <strong data-start=\"5875\" data-end=\"5882\">RUM<\/strong> (medici\u00f3n QoE real).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"5905\" data-end=\"5919\"><strong data-start=\"5905\" data-end=\"5919\">Semana 3\u20135<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"5920\" data-end=\"6083\"><li data-start=\"5920\" data-end=\"5993\"><p data-start=\"5922\" data-end=\"5993\">Piloto <strong data-start=\"5929\" data-end=\"5936\">AV1<\/strong> para VOD principales y eventos con alto tr\u00e1fico m\u00f3vil.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"5994\" data-end=\"6038\"><p data-start=\"5996\" data-end=\"6038\">Orquestaci\u00f3n <strong data-start=\"6009\" data-end=\"6022\">Multi-CDN<\/strong> por ISP\/pa\u00eds.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"6039\" data-end=\"6083\"><p data-start=\"6041\" data-end=\"6083\">PoC <strong data-start=\"6045\" data-end=\"6053\">SSAI<\/strong> con 2 segmentos demogr\u00e1ficos.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"6085\" data-end=\"6099\"><strong data-start=\"6085\" data-end=\"6099\">Semana 6\u20138<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"6100\" data-end=\"6195\"><li data-start=\"6100\" data-end=\"6142\"><p data-start=\"6102\" data-end=\"6142\">Canal <strong data-start=\"6108\" data-end=\"6116\">FAST<\/strong> con cat\u00e1logo existente.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"6143\" data-end=\"6195\"><p data-start=\"6145\" data-end=\"6195\">WebRTC para micro-interacciones (Q&amp;A, votaciones).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"6197\" data-end=\"6212\"><strong data-start=\"6197\" data-end=\"6212\">Semana 9\u201312<\/strong><\/p><ul data-start=\"6213\" data-end=\"6416\"><li data-start=\"6213\" data-end=\"6276\"><p data-start=\"6215\" data-end=\"6276\">IA: <strong data-start=\"6219\" data-end=\"6232\">upscaling<\/strong> en perfiles 720p\/1080p; auto-subtitulado.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"6277\" data-end=\"6349\"><p data-start=\"6279\" data-end=\"6349\">Seguridad: <strong data-start=\"6290\" data-end=\"6310\">tokens rotativos<\/strong> + watermarking en emisiones premium.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"6350\" data-end=\"6416\"><p data-start=\"6352\" data-end=\"6416\">Checklist de <strong data-start=\"6365\" data-end=\"6382\">accesibilidad<\/strong> (subt\u00edtulos, contraste, teclado).<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-start=\"6418\" data-end=\"6421\" \/><h2 data-start=\"6423\" data-end=\"6436\">Conclusi\u00f3n<\/h2><p data-start=\"6437\" data-end=\"6766\">En 2025 el streaming es <strong data-start=\"6461\" data-end=\"6505\">m\u00e1s r\u00e1pido, m\u00e1s n\u00edtido y m\u00e1s inteligente<\/strong>. La combinaci\u00f3n de <strong data-start=\"6525\" data-end=\"6536\">AV1\/VVC<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"6538\" data-end=\"6548\">HTTP\/3<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"6550\" data-end=\"6567\">LL-HLS\/WebRTC<\/strong>, <strong data-start=\"6569\" data-end=\"6589\">producci\u00f3n cloud<\/strong> y <strong data-start=\"6592\" data-end=\"6607\">capas de IA<\/strong> permite reducir costes sin sacrificar calidad ni interacci\u00f3n. Quien alinee tecnolog\u00eda con negocio (FAST, CTV ads, shoppable, comunidad) ganar\u00e1 alcance y ARPU.<\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}]";}s:13:"_thumbnail_id";a:1:{i:0;s:4:"8354";}s:10:"_edit_last";a:1:{i:0;s:1:"1";}s:13:"_aioseo_title";a:1:{i:0;N;}s:19:"_aioseo_description";a:1:{i:0;N;}s:16:"_aios